# Free Video & Photo Editor

A free, browser-based video and photo editor that allows you to trim videos, apply filters, and export media instantly â€” no downloads or installations needed. Designed for creators, students, and hobbyists, this tool makes professional-quality edits simple and accessible.

## Features

- Instant Preview: Upload videos or images and see them immediately.
- Trim Videos: Play only the desired portion by selecting start and end times.
- Apply Filters: Adjust brightness, contrast, and grayscale on videos and images.
- Export Media: Download edited content directly from your browser.
- Fully Frontend: Works entirely in-browser; no backend required.

## Usage

1. Upload a video or image.
2. Set start and end times for trimming.
3. Apply filters to enhance your media.
4. Export your edited file.

